LINUX / HOME ASSISTANT

# 1. Install nvm (once)
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
source ~/.bashrc   # or just open a new terminal

# 2. Install Node
nvm install 20

# 3. Flash (most sticks appear as /dev/ttyACM0)
npx @zwave-js/flash@latest /dev/ttyACM0 Zooz_ZST39_800LR_US_1.50.gbl --verbose

Or you can find the by-id location by typing in the path and hitting tab at  /dev/serial/by-id/
Example:  /dev/serial/by-id/usb-Zooz_800_Z-Wave_Stick_533D004242-if00
